{"tid":2382173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"join us~香港/外國/回流/想認識香港嘅你","createTime":"2021-01-27T06:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T04:02:13.000Z","uid":9178,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64d83a9ac51b5704734e18eb4353cecc58a15a1c","tid":2382173,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"逐步會轉去signal 稍安勿躁 比啲時間大家適應 互相遷就<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">香港人<br />\n喺外國嘅香港人<br />\n回流香港嘅香港人<br />\n非香港人但想了解香港嘅人（eg 台灣）<br />\n</span><br />\n呢個谷都歡迎你 希望大家可以知道更多唔同嘅野 識到更多朋友<br />\n<br />\n不論你好悶，係外國冇人傾計，返嚟香港後冇朋友，外國朋友想認識香港文化，呢到都十分啱你<br />\n<br />\n呢到絕不強逼你出聚，自由出聚。但強逼你吹水 唔出聚唔會踢 唔出聲會踢 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">谷內混合唔同國家嘅人（多數歐洲+香港+少量台灣人想認識香港）</span><br />\n<br />\n唔洗擔心時差，總有人陪到你<br />\n唔會揀人加，但set咗只可以填一次，所以要登入<br />\n擔心嘅，唔好加入<br />\n加人速度慢 要耐心等等<br />\n<br />\n#只係一個普通吹水谷 咁大個人 咩應該講 咩唔應該講 你自己知<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/gnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fgnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=6d866198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/gnsgfxkgu6Lqyjew9</a>"},{"pid":"1003ded9dc6c64be8f1157428ef5ac99505dcefa","tid":2382173,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"3eb559869ec92a3e2e5a125522f8404fb18d3fae","tid":2382173,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老豆"},{"pid":"b1d13d7d7efdf37544d8bdc6044fd13f3999cd66","tid":2382173,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:52:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母祖宗18代"},{"pid":"f7aa2a3d52c41d468b9b458688d25f001bfb95a9","tid":2382173,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"你老母比狗中出口爆"},{"pid":"9dc9f34f27f397695a875d0ce93593ebb5d24537","tid":2382173,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01